Title: Remarks on supersymmetric effective actions and supersymmetry breaking

Comments: 18 pages, Latex, Two references added, some minor changes and some

additional discussion in concluding section, cover letter removed!We discuss some issues related to the definition of different effectiveactions, in connection with the work on supersymmetric theories by Seiberg andcollaborators. We also comment on the possibility of extending this work tobroken supersymmetric theories.